# Snappy Platform - Design & Branding Guidelines

## Landing Page Status
**APPROVED** - The current landing page design is the reference for ALL subpages and extensions.

## Brand Identity

### Color Palette (Dark Theme - Default)
| Token | HSL | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-----|-------|
| --background | 230 25% 10% | #1A1A2E | Main background |
| --foreground | 40 20% 95% | #F5F3EF | Primary text |
| --card | 230 25% 14% | #232340 | Cards, panels |
| --primary | 142 71% 45% | #4ADE80 | Snappy Green (CTAs, highlights) |
| --secondary | 200 45% 30% | #3B6B7C | Teal accent (logo rim) |
| --accent | 35 30% 75% | #D4C5A9 | Tan/cream complement |
| --muted | 230 20% 20% | #2A2A3D | Muted backgrounds |
| --border | 230 20% 20% | #2A2A3D | Borders |

### Typography
- **Font Family**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Font Smoothing**: antialiased, grayscale
- **Hero Title**: 5xl-7xl bold
- **Section Title**: 3xl-4xl bold
- **Body**: Base size, muted-foreground color

### Visual Effects
- **Glow Effect (.glow-green)**:
  ```css
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.5),
               0 0 40px rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.3);
  ```
- **Border Radius**: 0.5rem (8px) standard, rounded-xl (16px) for cards

### Logo
- **Location**: /public/images/logo.png
- **Dimensions**: 240x240px (responsive scaling)
- **Border Radius**: rounded-xl (16px)

## Design Patterns

### Card Pattern
```css
background: var(--card);
padding: 24px;
border-radius: 12px;
border: 1px solid var(--border);
```

### Button Pattern (Primary)
```css
background: var(--primary);
color: var(--background);
border-radius: 8px;
font-weight: 600;
transition: all 0.2s;
```
Hover: `background: var(--primary) / 0.9`

### Icon Circles
```css
width: 64px;
height: 64px;
background: var(--primary) / 0.2;
border-radius: 50%;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
```

## Subpages Checklist
All subpages MUST include:
- [ ] Logo in header (40x40px)
- [ ] Dark navy background (#1A1A2E)
- [ ] Snappy Green for primary actions (#4ADE80)
- [ ] Inter font family
- [ ] Consistent spacing (py-24 sections, gap-6 grids)
- [ ] Border-border styling on cards

## Chrome Extension Requirements
The Chrome extension MUST match the landing page branding:
- [ ] Same color palette (dark navy + snappy green)
- [ ] Include logo.png in extension
- [ ] Inter font (via CSS import or embed)
- [ ] Same button styling
- [ ] Same glow effects where applicable
- [ ] Consistent border-radius (8px)

